<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Modify</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/9156B30C-7578-4C37-A0A3-5CD259467220" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Modify">
					<arm />
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/arm" required="true()" />
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="arm-label">
						<value>Enter Study Arm</value>
					</text>
					<text id="arm-arm_a-label">
						<value>a</value>
					</text>
					<text id="arm-arm_b-label">
						<value>b</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<select1 ref="/data/arm">
			<label ref="jr:itext('arm-label')" />
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('arm-arm_a-label')" />
				<value>arm_a</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('arm-arm_b-label')" />
				<value>arm_b</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
	</h:body>
</h:html>
_attachments.2154a47f01f14a0696467e86943612c9f3e2a9e0:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>New Form</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/0C7E656F-DD1D-4B0F-9330-70535D4EE3A0" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="New Form">
					<q_text />
					<q_single_select />
					<q_multi_select />
					<q_int />
					<q_float />
					<q_long />
					<q_date />
					<q_time />
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_text" type="xsd:string" constraint=". = "abc"" jr:constraintMsg="jr:itext('q_text-constraintMsg')" required="true()" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_single_select" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_multi_select" required="true()" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_int" type="xsd:int" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_float" type="xsd:double" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_long" type="xsd:long" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_date" type="xsd:date" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/q_time" type="xsd:time" />
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="q_text-label">
						<value>text</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_text-constraintMsg">
						<value>Expected "abc"</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_single_select-label">
						<value>single select</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_single_select-a-label">
						<value>a</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_single_select-b-label">
						<value>b</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_single_select-c-label">
						<value>c</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_single_select-d-label">
						<value>d</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_multi_select-label">
						<value>multi select</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_multi_select-a-label">
						<value>a</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_multi_select-b-label">
						<value>b</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_multi_select-c-label">
						<value>c</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_multi_select-d-label">
						<value>d</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_int-label">
						<value>int</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_float-label">
						<value>float</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_long-label">
						<value>long</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_date-label">
						<value>date</value>
					</text>
					<text id="q_time-label">
						<value>time</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<input ref="/data/q_text">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_text-label')" />
		</input>
		<select1 ref="/data/q_single_select">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_single_select-label')" />
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_single_select-a-label')" />
				<value>a</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_single_select-b-label')" />
				<value>b</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_single_select-c-label')" />
				<value>c</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_single_select-d-label')" />
				<value>d</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<select ref="/data/q_multi_select">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_multi_select-label')" />
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_multi_select-a-label')" />
				<value>a</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_multi_select-b-label')" />
				<value>b</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_multi_select-c-label')" />
				<value>c</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('q_multi_select-d-label')" />
				<value>d</value>
			</item>
		</select>
		<input ref="/data/q_int">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_int-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/q_float">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_float-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/q_long">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_long-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/q_date">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_date-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/q_time">
			<label ref="jr:itext('q_time-label')" />
		</input>
	</h:body>
</h:html>

<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Create</h:title>

					<participant_id />
					<arm />

			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/participant_id" type="xsd:string" required="true()" />

					</text>
					<text id="arm-arm_b-label">
						<value>b</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<input ref="/data/participant_id">
			<label ref="jr:itext('participant_id-label')" />
		</input>
		<select1 ref="/data/arm">
			<label ref="jr:itext('arm-label')" />
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('arm-arm_a-label')" />
				<value>arm_a</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('arm-arm_b-label')" />
				<value>arm_b</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
	</h:body>
</h:html>
